      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>Our mission is to simplify hiring workflows for modern companies.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 16px;">We believe that great companies are built by great people. Our platform is designed to eliminate the friction in recruitment, enabling teams to focus on what truly matters — finding and hiring exceptional talent. At Smart Hire, we're committed to making hiring transparent, efficient, and human-centered.</p>
